Log Inspector :

Debug | View Log Panels :

Stack Tree :  if one class calls a second class, the second class is shown as the child of the first.
Execution Stack : log entry, followed by the operation that called it.
Execution Log : Displays every action that occurred during the execution of your code
Source : Displays the contents of the source file
Execution Overview : execution time and heap size

